VA few days after my husband Paul was diagnosed with stage IV lung cancer,
p4
aVwe were lying in our bed at home,
p5
aVand Paul said,
p6
aV"It's going to be OK."
p7
aVAnd I remember answering back,
p8
aV"Yes.
p9
aVWe just don't know what OK means yet."
