aa(lp11
VPaul and I had met as first-year medical students at Yale.
p12
aVHe was smart and kind and super funny.
p13
aVHe used to keep a gorilla suit in the trunk of his car,
p14
aVand he'd say, "It's for emergencies only."
p15
aa(lp16
V(Laughter)
