aa(lp18
VI fell in love with Paul as I watched the care he took with his patients.
p19
aVHe stayed late talking with them,
p20
aVseeking to understand the experience of illness
p21
aVand not just its technicalities.
p22
aVHe later told me he fell in love with me
p23
aVwhen he saw me cry over an EKG of a heart that had ceased beating.
p24
aVWe didn't know it yet,
p25
aVbut even in the heady days of young love,
p26
aVwe were learning how to approach suffering together.
