aa(lp28
VWe got married and became doctors.
p29
aVI was working as an internist
p30
aVand Paul was finishing his training as a neurosurgeon
p31
aVwhen he started to lose weight.
p32
aVHe developed excruciating back pain and a cough that wouldn't go away.
p33
aVAnd when he was admitted to the hospital,
p34
